title: Stardom Goddesses of Stardom Tag League 2025 - Day 7
overview: The seventh night of Stardom Goddesses of Stardom Tag League 2025 took place on November 16, 2025 at Chateraise Gateaux Kingdom Sapporo in Sapporo, Hokkaido, Japan, and was headlined by a Block A match between God's Eye (Ami Sourei & Lady C) and HATE (Konami & Rina).
